{"tid":118693,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有無做過美容/纖體既絲打？(￣∇￣)","createTime":"2017-02-13T08:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T07:28:02.000Z","uid":83809,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0bfee64c1698fd83301cd15fb3109b4ec90f87ef","tid":118693,"uid":83809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位絲打有咩好介紹？<br />\n去過幾間，出名同無咁出名都試過，其實係咪間間都咁Hard sell，唔Join又黑面，前言不對後語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有絕望感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96448e30939faf796d2caf35978114d651ce03ea","tid":118693,"uid":83809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:40:43.000Z","msg":"去過Dream Beaxxx pro，呀劉佩玥代言諗住ok掛(唔知有無打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )。<br />\n第一次去有試做價既，book個時直接問如果之後做係幾錢一次同可唔可以逐次比，條友話可以同埋都係同試做價一樣。<br />\n<br />\n入到去填form個啲正常野就唔多講，終於開始做，一開始就講下咩步驟程序都好正常，之後另一個人入左黎(真係負責做個個)，一個負責講一個負責做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講咩？梗係講叫你join plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 面同纖體我都有試做，就一路up野話依家join呢個最平架喇乜乜乜，又問我知唔知單次係幾錢。問番佢係咪都係試做價咁多錢，佢即刻話個個價係要買50格先有架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一陣伏味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係咁講&quot;咁唔洗喇，我都咁多錢住&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢繼續無視，係咁講可以分期12同24個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢塊面仲要越來越西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實個treatment做左半粒中倒就完，佢講野都成粒半中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咁講有唔同plan可以買少啲遲啲再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放過我喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後梗係無join，佢仲要勁厚臉皮問我佢地服務點，方唔方便填張意見卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就寫左幾句話幫我做treatment個個人手勢幾好既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下面P.S. No Hardsell pls.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即時爽曬"},{"pid":"6d86db05e239df644e77549e67b78e3f041f8931","tid":118693,"uid":44491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T07:28:02.000Z","msg":"去過三間，sell就一定間間都有<br />\n我份人耳仔軟，三間都有join過course<br />\n其中兩間感覺幾好，雖然周不時都sell我，但唔買既話都唔會留難我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一間aqxxxxus就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就咁易google都搵到幾個負評<br />\n都幾hard sell，煩到嘔，我都唔明點解我去左咁多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次買treatment都話可以分幾期俾（每次上去逐少俾cash/碌eps咁，我堅持唔搞credit card自動分期），但下次上去第一句就chur我俾晒啲尾數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次撚次都係咁，雖然實際上真係可以分期既，但咁既態度真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上有時同啲美容師唔太岩傾就無再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前有去yxu beauty<br />\n覺得效果唔錯又唔hard sell，同埋學生價好似都唔貴<br />\n不過有去開其他美容院就費事join咁多間，做晒咁多次treatment就算<br />\n<br />\n而家唯一keep住去果間好似係無咁出名既，e字頭係tst<br />\n之前開左分店，但我上佢fb又淨係見到tst既地址，唔知係執左定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢間啲手勢好似幾⋯⋯特別？之前果兩間做facial去黑頭果陣都淨係會feel到痛既，但呢間有時會覺得鼻入面有少少痕想打乞嚏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不時會sell我試做其他野，不過唔想既話拒絕多兩次就無野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分期俾錢又唔會chur住你俾，每次俾好少都無所謂<br />\n介紹過朋友上去免費試做脫毛，結果佢join晒脫毛同facial，去得仲密過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有興趣我可以介紹絲打免費試做treatment，唔岩都唔會話嘥左啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}